casebody.data:
SHEA, Respondent, v. GREAT CAMP OF KNIGHTS OF MACCABEES FOR NEW YORK, Appellant. (Supreme Court, Appellate Division, Fourth Department. July 26, 1898.)

Action by Michael fi. Shea, as administrator, etc., against the Great Camp of the Knights of the Maccabees for New York. No opinion. Motion denied.

See 52 N. Y. Supp. 333.
